ed="T" n="0783b17"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0783b17"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000014540"><placeName>天台</placeName><placeName>紫凝山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010623">慧恭</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0783b18"/><persName key="A010623">釋慧恭</persName>，俗姓<name>羅</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000017166"><placeName>福州</placeName><placeName>閩</placeName></placeName>人也。家傳儒素，<lb
ed="T" n="0783b19"/>不交非類。母妊之初，夢所居湧出浮圖，上<lb
ed="T" n="0783b20"/>參于天。迨<persName key="A010623">恭</persName>誕生，嶷然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1447"/>聰悟。<date key="j20264032026768" from-iso="+0836-01-01" to-iso="+0836-12-31">年十七</date>，舉進<lb
ed="T" n="0783b21"/>士，名隨計車<ptr type="glossary" target="#g921"/>。將到<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京闕</ref>，因遊<placeName key="PL000000042514"><placeName>終南山</placeName><placeName>奉日<lb
ed="T" n="0783b22"/>寺</placeName></placeName>，目祖師遺像，釋然世<anchor xml:id="beg0783sgsz9"/>網<anchor xml:id="end0783sgsz9"/>，遂求出家。操執<lb
ed="T" n="0783b23"/>僧事，備歷艱辛。<date key="j20282602028642" from-iso="+0841-01-31" to-iso="+0842-02-17">二十有二</date>，適值新創<placeName key="PL000000057259">安國<lb
ed="T" n="0783b24"/>寺</placeName>受具足戒。尋乃遊方，緣嶮涉荒，而無難<lb
ed="T" n="0783b25"/>色。嘗遇黑蛇傷指，不求醫而毒螫自銷。見<lb
ed="T" n="0783b26"/>魑魅占山，諭罪福而妖物遄息。至<placeName key="PL000000029435"><placeName>武陵</placeName><placeName>德<lb
ed="T" n="0783b27"/>山</placeName></placeName>，詣<persName key="A003868">宣鑒<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，領會風飛，由茲道合。因挂<lb
ed="T" n="0783b28"/>錫，施門人禮。<persName key="A003868">鑒<roleName>公</roleName></persName>順世後，遊<placeName key="PL000000020056">玉山</placeName>。至<placeName key="PL000000020175">信州</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0783b29"/>刺史營<placeName key="PL000000020132">西禪院</placeName>而禮之，其徒數百人。居歲<pb ed="T" n="0783c" xml:id="T50.2061.0783c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0783c01"/>餘，以郛郭喧繁，復入<placeName key="PL000000018481"><placeName>福州</placeName><placeName>長溪</placeName><placeName>馬冠山</placeName></placeName>。自<lb
ed="T" n="0783c02"/><placeName key="PL000000018481">馬冠</placeName>抵<placeName key="PL000000017887"><placeName>泉州</placeName><placeName>富陽山</placeName></placeName>，所至之所，檀施<ptr type="glossary" target="#g237"/>臻集，<lb
ed="T" n="0783c03"/>徒侶解鉢，禪坊立就，其為士庶嚮奉如此。<lb
ed="T" n="0783c04"/><date from-iso="+0894-02-14" key="j20476322047985" to-iso="+0895-02-02"><name>景福</name>三年</date><ptr target="#n1681"/>，與門人遊<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>，州牧<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName><persName key="A010633">杜雄</persName>留<lb
ed="T" n="0783c05"/>之而止。<persName key="A010633">杜</persName>因創<placeName key="PL000000014758">瑞龍院</placeName>於<placeName key="PL000000014540">紫凝山</placeName>，祈<persName key="A010623">恭</persName>興<lb
ed="T" n="0783c06"/>揚法席，以悟淪迷。緇俗雲馳，香花山積。<date when-iso="+0903-12-28" key="j20512352051235"><name>天<lb
ed="T" n="0783c07"/>復</name>三年癸亥十二月<supplied resp="sgsz">二日</supplied></date>午時<ptr target="#n1682"/>，命眾聲鐘，顧瞻<lb
ed="T" n="0783c08"/>左右，促言云去。加趺瞑目，儼然而化，春秋八<lb
ed="T" n="0783c09"/>十四，僧夏六十二。闡圓頓之宗，居道德之<lb
ed="T" n="0783c10"/>最，歿無易名，塔無題<anchor xml:id="beg0783007"/>榜<anchor xml:id="end0783007"/>，足見浮名為桎<lb
ed="T" n="0783c11"/>梏耳。門人上足<persName key="A023031">師遂</persName>植松負土，力崇塔廟，<lb
ed="T" n="0783c12"/>所謂法空不壞因緣矣。因緣有之，孝行曷<lb
ed="T" n="0783c13"/>傷于道<anchor xml:id="beg0783008"/>云<anchor xml:id="end0783008"/>。</p>
